title: Use ref for isCheckingAuth to prevent excess check calls
body: `useAuth` fires an extra call because state doesn't flush until the next tick. The double firing causes 500 and 401 errors on the session and the user getting logged out inconsistently (at least on SQLite backend, haven't tried others). Moving it to a ref fixes the issue.
